"Memory of Data"
On May 16, Shanghai Airport announced that the number of aircraft takeoffs and landings at Pudong International Airport in April increased by 725.97% year-on-year;
passenger throughput increased by 8155.87% year-on-year.
Hongqiao International Airport increased by 6273.26% year-on-year;
passenger throughput increased by 28057.71% year-on-year.
